text.section:
The application for a grant shall include:
Project plans for the work to be carried out;
A statement listing the personnel employed or to be employed at the federally qualified health center, including all remuneration and perquisites for personal services and all other expenses paid or to be paid to the personnel;
All other expenses incurred or to be incurred in operating the federally qualified health center; and
The schedule of rates charged or to be charged for services rendered.
